  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 27-7-22.39, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH AUTHORIZES INCOME TAX CREDITS AND AD VALOREM TAX CREDITS FOR VOLUNTARY CASH CONTRIBUTIONS BY INDIVIDUAL TAXPAYERS TO QUALIFYING CHARITABLE ORGANIZATIONS AND QUALIFYING FOSTER CARE CHARITABLE ORGANIZATIONS, TO AUTHORIZE INCOME TAX CREDITS FOR VOLUNTARY CASH CONTRIBUTIONS BY CERTAIN OTHER TAXPAYERS TO QUALIFYING CHARITABLE ORGANIZATIONS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
